listName: End User Experience & Adoption Projects on Open Source Observer
listDescription: All OSS projects in the 'End User Experience & Adoption' impact category that had their first commit before the start of RetroPGF3 and haven't appeared on other lists. This list is powered by Open Source Observer.
impactEvaluationDescription: This list awards 75K OP tokens to any RetroPGF3 project in the 'End User Experience & Adoption' category that is represented on https://opensource.observer and hasn't appeared on more than 3 OSO-powered lists. Only projects with unique, public GitHub repos included in their application have been indexed by OSO. It awards additional tokens to projects based on the number of monthly active users they have on OP Mainnet. Finally, projects targeting end users on Base, Farcaster, and Zora networks also receive a 10K OP bonus. Note: lists generated by the OSO team do not include OSO in them in order to comply with voting rules, so please consider adding our project to your ballot separately. Always remember to DYOR before voting: project data is never complete and never tells the full story!
